data.title: Population: Taiwan Area: Taoyuan City
data.meta_description: Population: Taiwan Area: Taoyuan City data was reported at 2,217.776 Person th in Nov 2018. This records an increase from the previous number of 2,215.615 Person th for Oct 2018. Population: Taiwan Area: Taoyuan City data is updated monthly, averaging 1,865.923 Person th (Median) from Jan 1992 to Nov 2018, with 323 observations. The data reached an all-time high of 2,217.776 Person th in Nov 2018 and a record low of 1,386.492 Person th in Jan 1992. Population: Taiwan Area: Taoyuan City data remains active status in CEIC and is reported by Ministry of the Interior. The data is categorized under Global Database’s Taiwan – Table TW.G001: Population.
